name: AG Jewelry Black Resin Kufi Jesus Piece
description: One of the most recognizable and iconic status symbols of Hip-Hop could undeniably be "The Jesus Piece." Through the decades, the many faces, verses, and variations have also established The Jesus Piece as a timeless staple. We've revisited and refined the design of the original "kufi" Jesus, and have resurrected it in an unconventional new medium. All our pieces are hand cast and finished in a proprietary resin composite. The integrated bail design is reinforced with a brass grommet. *Includes 36in. black metal ball chain.
